<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَكُرِهَ:</span> إِنِ اسْتَتَمَّ قَائِماً.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَحَرُمَ وَبَطَلَتْ:</span> إِنْ شَرَعَ فِي القِرَاءَةِ، لَا إِنْ نَسِيَ أَوْ جَهِلَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَيَتْبَعُ مَأْمُومٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَيَجِبُ السُّجُودُ لِذَلِكَ مُطْلَقاً.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَيَبْنِي عَلَى اليَقِينِ - وَهُوَ الأَقَلُّ -: مَنْ شَكَّ فِي رُكْنٍ، أَوْ عَدَدٍ. واللهُ أَعْلَمُ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> آكَدُ صَلَاةِ تَطَوُّعٍ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> كُسُوفٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> فَاسْتِسْقَاءٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> فَتَرَاوِيحُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> فَوِتْرٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَوَقْتُهُ:</span> مِنْ صَلَاةِ العِشَاءِ إِلَى الفَجْرِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأَقَلُّهُ:</span> رَكْعَةٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (والله أعلم) سقطت من (أ) و (ب) و (د).</p> </div>